            </h3>
 
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-8">
                <div>
                    Copyright Â© 2016 - {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} Urban Style Publicity, S.L.
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-x-8 gap-y-4 flex-wrap">
                    {% include 'partials/legal-links.html.twig' %}
